WITH t as (
WITH s as (
WITH ab as (
WITH a as (
WITH w1 as (
SELECT
            SOLSEG.SSOLICIT,
            SOLSEG.CUSUARI,
            SOLSEG.FALTA,
            TO_CHAR(SOLSEG.FALTA,'YYYY')ANYO,
            TO_CHAR(SOLSEG.FALTA,'MM')MES,
            TO_CHAR(SOLSEG.FALTA,'DD')DIA,
            SOLSEG.CRAMO,
            SOLSEG.CMODALI,
            SOLSEG.CTIPSEG,
            SOLSEG.CCOLECT,
            SOLSEG.CACTIVI,
            SOLSEG.SPRODUC,
            SOLSEG.CAGENTE,
            TO_NUMBER(SUBSTRING(SOLSEG.CAGENTE,LENGTH(SOLSEG.CAGENTE)-2,3),'999') A_ID_SUCURSAL,
        	(SELECT P.TAPELLI FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_AGENTES  A LEFT JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_PERSONAS  P ON A.SPERSON= P.SPERSON  AND A.CTIPAGE=1 WHERE A.CAGENTE = '00000'|| SUBSTRING(SOLSEG.CAGENTE,LENGTH(SOLSEG.CAGENTE)-2,3) )A_NOMBRE_SUCURSAL,
            CAST(SOLSEG.SSEGURO AS NUMERIC(25,0)) AS SSEGURO,
            SOLSEG.CRFAAGE,
            SUBSTRING(SOLASEG.NNUMNIF,1,LENGTH(SOLASEG.NNUMNIF)-1)RUT_ASEGURADO,
            SOLASEG.SPERSON,
            AUTVER.CMARCA,
	        AUTVER.SMODELO,
            SOLAUT.NANOFAB
FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLSEGUROS  SOLSEG 
    	INNER JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLASEGURADOS  SOLASEG ON SOLSEG.SSOLICIT = SOLASEG.SSOLICIT AND NORDEN =(SELECT  MAX(NORDEN) FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLASEGURADOS  WHERE SSOLICIT=SOLSEG.SSOLICIT)
    	LEFT  JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_PERSONAS  PER ON SOLASEG.SPERSON =PER.SPERSON
    	INNER JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLAUTRIESGOS  SOLAUT ON
                SOLSEG.SSOLICIT=SOLAUT.SSOLICIT AND
                SOLAUT.NRIESGO = (SELECT  MAX(NORDEN) FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLASEGURADOS  WHERE SSOLICIT=SOLSEG.SSOLICIT)
    	INNER JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_AUTVERSIONES  AUTVER ON SOLAUT.CVERSION = AUTVER.CVERSION
    	INNER JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_AGENTES  AGE ON AGE.CAGENTE = SOLSEG.CAGENTE
WHERE SOLSEG.CRAMO = 6
AND SOLSEG.FALTA BETWEEN TO_DATE('01/01/2018', 'dd/MM/yyyy HH24:MI:SS')  AND getdate()
)
 
select * from (
select a.*, b.cnt, 0 as robot from (
(SELECT * from w1) a
left join
(select rut_asegurado,mes, count(1) as cnt from w1 group by rut_asegurado, mes) b
on
a.rut_asegurado=b.rut_asegurado and
a.mes=b.mes) )
 
),
 
b as (
 
select * from
(
SELECT  CAST(SEG.SSEGURO as NUMERIC(25,0)) as B_SSEGURO,
    	CAST(SEG.NPOLIZA as NUMERIC(25,0)) as B_NPOLIZA,
    	SEG.NCERTIF as B_NCERTIF,
    	SEG.SPRODUC as B_SPRODUC,
    	SEG.IPRIANUSEG as B_IPIRIANUSEG,
        GARANSEG.IPRITAR as B_IPRITAR,
        GARANSEG.PDTOCOM as B_PDTOCOM,
    	GARANSEG.IFRANQUSEG as B_IFRAQUSEG,
    	SEG.FEMISIO as B_FEMISIO,
    	SEG.FEFECTO as B_FEFECTO,
        DECODE(SEG.cduraci, 3, SEG.fvencim, SEG.fcarpro) B_FIN_VIG,
    	CASE WHEN SEG.CDURACI = 3 THEN SEG.FVENCIM ELSE   SEG.FCARPRO END B_FVENCIM,
    	SEG.CACTIVI as B_CACTIVI,
    	SEG.FANULAC as B_FANULAC,
    	TI.TTITULO as B_TTITULO,
    	SEG.CAGENTE as B_CAGENTE,
        TO_NUMBER(SUBSTRING(SEG.CAGENTE,LENGTH(SEG.CAGENTE)-2,3),'999') B_ID_SUCURSAL, 
    	(SELECT P.TAPELLI FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_AGENTES  A LEFT JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_PERSONAS  P ON A.SPERSON= P.SPERSON  AND A.CTIPAGE=1 WHERE A.CAGENTE = '00000'||SUBSTRING(SEG.CAGENTE,LENGTH(SEG.CAGENTE)-2,3) )B_NOMBRE_SUCURSAL,
    	PER.TBUSCAR as B_TBUSCAR,
        SUBSTRING(PER.NNUMNIF,1,LENGTH(PER.NNUMNIF)-1)B_NNUMNIF,
    	PER.SPERSON as B_SPERSON,
    	AUTVER.CMARCA as B_CMARCA,
    	AUTVER.SMODELO as B_SMODELO,  	
    	AUT.NANOFAB as B_NANOFAB,
    	SEG.CSITUAC as B_CSITUAC,                          	
    	1 EMISION
FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SEGUROS  SEG
                            LEFT JOIN ( SELECT 	T1.SSEGURO,
                            SUM(IPRITAR)IPRITAR,
                            SUM(IPRIANUSEG)IPRIANUSEG,
                            MAX(IFRANQUSEG)IFRANQUSEG,
                            MAX(PDTOCOM) PDTOCOM
                            FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_GARANSEG  T1 INNER JOIN (SELECT SSEGURO,MAX(NMOVIMI)NMOVIMI
                            FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_GARANSEG 
                            GROUP BY SSEGURO) T2 ON T1.SSEGURO = T2.SSEGURO AND T1.NMOVIMI = T2.NMOVIMI
                            GROUP BY T1.SSEGURO)
                            GARANSEG ON SEG.SSEGURO = GARANSEG.SSEGURO
                            INNER JOIN (SELECT  SSEGURO,SPERSON ,MAX(NORDEN)NORDEN FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_ASEGURADOS  WHERE FFECFIN IS NULL GROUP BY SSEGURO,SPERSON )ASEG ON SEG.SSEGURO = ASEG.SSEGURO
                            INNER JOIN (                                                                                          
                            SELECT A1.CVERSION,A1.SSEGURO,A1.NANOFAB
                            FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_AUTRIESGOS  A1 INNER JOIN   --cdp_ods
                            (SELECT SSEGURO,MAX(NMOVIMI)NMOVIMI,MAX(NRIESGO)NRIESGO FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_AUTRIESGOS  GROUP BY SSEGURO )A2  ON A1.SSEGURO= A2.SSEGURO AND A1.NRIESGO=A2.NRIESGO
                            GROUP BY A1.CVERSION,A1.SSEGURO,A1.NANOFAB                                                                                                                                       
                            ) AUT ON SEG.SSEGURO=AUT.SSEGURO 
                            INNER JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_AUTVERSIONES  AUTVER ON AUT.CVERSION = AUTVER.CVERSION
                            INNER JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_AGENTES  AGE ON AGE.CAGENTE = SEG.CAGENTE
                            INNER JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_PERSONAS  PER ON PER.SPERSON = ASEG.SPERSON
                            LEFT JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_TITULOPRO  TI ON TI.CCOLECT = SEG.CCOLECT AND TI.CMODALI= SEG.CMODALI AND TI.CTIPSEG = SEG.CTIPSEG AND TI.CRAMO= SEG.CRAMO                                                                         
WHERE
FEFECTO BETWEEN TO_DATE('01/01/2018', 'dd/MM/yyyy HH24:MI:SS') AND getdate() AND
SEG.CRAMO =6 AND
NCERTIF >0 AND
SPRODUC = 760)
)
 
SELECT a.*,b.*,
datediff (day,a.FALTA,b.b_FEFECTO) as diffdays
FROM a LEFT JOIN b
ON  a.RUT_ASEGURADO = b.B_NNUMNIF
AND a.CMARCA = b.B_CMARCA
AND a.SMODELO = b.B_SMODELO
AND a.NANOFAB = b.B_NANOFAB
),
 
c as (
SELECT SSOLICIT as C_SSOLICIT, PDTOCOM as C_PDTOCOM from
(
SELECT T1.SSOLICIT,nvl(MAX(PDTOCOM)/100,0)PDTOCOM
FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLGARANSEG  T1 INNER JOIN
(
SELECT SSOLICIT FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLSEGUROS  WHERE
FALTA >= TO_DATE('01/01/2018', 'dd/MM/yyyy HH24:MI:SS')
) T2 ON T1.SSOLICIT = T2.SSOLICIT
GROUP BY T1.SSOLICIT
)),
 
d as (
SELECT T1.SSOLICIT as D_SSOLICIT,
MAX(CASE WHEN NPROP =1 THEN CRESPUE END) D_DED_00,
MAX(CASE WHEN NPROP =2 THEN CRESPUE END) D_DED_03,
MAX(CASE WHEN NPROP =3 THEN CRESPUE END) D_DED_05,
MAX(CASE WHEN NPROP =4 THEN CRESPUE END) D_DED_10
FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLPREGUNSEGPROP  T1 INNER JOIN 
(SELECT SSOLICIT FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_SOLSEGUROS  WHERE FALTA >= TO_DATE('01/01/2018', 'dd/MM/yyyy HH24:MI:SS') )
T2 ON T1.SSOLICIT = T2.SSOLICIT
WHERE CPREGUN =1000
GROUP BY T1.SSOLICIT
),
 
e as (
WITH PAR_V_COND as(
SELECT pcr.cregla as CREGLA,pcr.scondreg as SCONDREG, cp.cpregun as CPREGUN, pcr.crespue as CRESPUE, pcr.nvalinf as NVALINF,pcr.nvalsup as NVALSUP,p.cidioma as CIDIOMA,
   	(p.tpregun || DECODE(pcr.CRESPUE,NULL,' ' || DECODE(pcr.nvalsup,NULL, (pcr.nvalinf :: varchar), (pcr.nvalinf :: varchar) || ' - ' || ((pcr.nvalsup || ' ') :: varchar)),
                                    	': ' || (SELECT TRESPUE FROM cdp_ods.sisaxis_RESPUESTAS  WHERE CPREGUN = p.cpregun AND CRESPUE = pcr.crespue AND CIDIOMA = p.cidioma))) as TCONDIC
FROM cdp_ods.sisaxis_preguntas p ,cdp_ods.sisaxis_codipregun cp,cdp_ods.sisaxis_par_condic_reglas pcr
WHERE p.cpregun = cp.cpregun
  AND	pcr.cpregun = p.cpregun
)
 
SELECT DISTINCT
--REPLACE ((SELECT TBUSCAR FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_PERSONAS  PER, cdp_ods.SISAXIS_USUARIOS  U WHERE PER.SPERSON=U.SPERSON AND U.CUSUARI=P.CUSUARI), '##', '')  E_NOMBRE_USUARIO, /*commented as part of DID_238*/
translate ((SELECT TBUSCAR FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_PERSONAS  PER, cdp_ods.SISAXIS_USUARIOS  U WHERE PER.SPERSON=U.SPERSON AND U.CUSUARI=P.CUSUARI), '#', '')  E_NOMBRE_USUARIO,  /* added as part of DID_238*/
    	P.CUSUARI as E_CUSUARI, P.CPERFIL as E_CPERFIL ,
    	(SELECT TPERFIL FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_DESPERFIL  WHERE CPERFIL=P.CPERFIL) E_DESC_PERFIL_USUARIO,
    	(SELECT NVALSUP FROM PAR_V_COND A1, cdp_ods.SISAXIS_DETASOCCOND  B1, cdp_ods.SISAXIS_CODIASOCCOND  C1
    	WHERE A1.CREGLA = 6000
    	AND A1.CPREGUN = 5013
    	AND A1.SCONDREG = B1.SCONDREG
    	AND B1.SASOCIA = C1.SASOCIA
    	AND C1.CPERFEXG = P.CPERFIL ) E_DESCUENTO_PERMITIDO
   FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_PAR_PERFILES_USUARIO  P, cdp_ods.SISAXIS_USU_DATOS  D
   WHERE  D.CUSUARI=P.CUSUARI
   AND D.CACTIVO='S' AND  P.CRAMO=6 AND P.ENTORNO=4
   ORDER BY E_CPERFIL
 
),
f as (
SELECT   A.CAGENTE as F_CAGENTE,  
     	SubString(P.NNUMNIF,1,Length(P.NNUMNIF)-1) +  SubString(P.NNUMNIF,Length(P.NNUMNIF),1)  F_RUT_CORREDOR,
         REPLACE(TBUSCAR,'#','') F_NOMBRE_CORREDOR
FROM cdp_ods.SISAXIS_AGENTES  A INNER JOIN cdp_ods.SISAXIS_PERSONAS  P ON A.SPERSON = P.SPERSON
),
g as (
SELECT CAST(CAST(sciclo AS NUMERIC(38,0)) AS VARCHAR) AS sciclo, count(1) as sciclo_count
from cdp_ods.sisaxis_cmi_propuesta  where csistema=1 and ctipdoc=1 and npoliza is not null and npoliza > 0 group by sciclo -- and npoliza > 0
)
 
 
select i.* from (
select h.*, lob.dim_lob_key, ins.mdik, bro.dim_broker_key, suc.dim_branch_office_key
from (
select abcdef.*, g.* from (
select abcde.*,f.*, cast('axis' as varchar(12)) as src_sys_cd, cast(0 as INT) as tipo_corredor, cast(0 as INT) as tipo_nego,
cast(1 as INT) as tipo_emission, max_sid, cast('web' as VARCHAR(8)) as quote_source
from (
select abcd.*,e.*
from (
select abc.*,d.*
from (
select ab1.*,c.*
from (
select X.*,Y.B_max_sseguro
from (
(select * from ab) X
LEFT JOIN
(select B_NNUMNIF, B_CMARCA, B_SMODELO, B_NANOFAB, MAX(B_SSEGURO) as B_max_sseguro
from ab where diffdays>=0 AND diffdays<=30 AND CUSUARI <> 'FPIAXIS2' AND CUSUARI <> 'ANIDA1' group by B_NNUMNIF, B_CMARCA, B_SMODELO, B_NANOFAB) Y
ON  X.B_NNUMNIF = Y.B_NNUMNIF
AND X.B_CMARCA = Y.B_CMARCA
AND X.B_SMODELO = Y.B_SMODELO
AND X.B_NANOFAB = Y.B_NANOFAB
AND X.SPRODUC = 760
AND X.diffdays>=0
AND X.diffdays<=30
AND X.B_SSEGURO = Y.B_max_sseguro
AND X.CUSUARI <> 'FPIAXIS2'
AND X.CUSUARI <> 'ANIDA1'
)
) ab1
left join c on
ab1.SSOLICIT = c.C_SSOLICIT ) abc
left join d on
abc.SSOLICIT = d.D_SSOLICIT ) abcd
left join e on
abcd.CUSUARI = e.E_CUSUARI) abcde
left join f on
abcde.CAGENTE = f.F_CAGENTE
left join
(select 1 dummy, max(fact_quote_key) max_sid from cdp_dwh.fact_quotation_t_test )LKP_MAX_KEY
on LKP_MAX_KEY.dummy=1 ) abcdef
left join g on
abcdef.CRFAAGE = g.sciclo
) h
left join (select * from cdp_dwh.dim_lob_t where src_sys_cd = 'axis') lob
on h.cramo = lob.lob_cd AND h.cusuari <> 'FPAXIS2' and h.cusuari <> 'ANIDA1'
left join /*(select insured_rut_num, max(dim_insured_key) as mdik  from cdp_dwh.dim_insured_t where src_sys_cd = 'axis' group by insured_rut_num) ins
on h.rut_asegurado = SUBSTRING(ins.insured_rut_num,1,LENGTH(ins.insured_rut_num)-1)*/
/* Modified as part of DID-234 */
(select 
    SUBSTRING(insured_rut_num, 1,LENGTH(insured_rut_num)-1) as rut_insured, 
    max( dim_insured_key ) as mdik  
  from 
    cdp_dwh.dim_insured_t 
  where 
    src_sys_cd = 'axis' 
  group by 
    SUBSTRING(insured_rut_num, 1,LENGTH(insured_rut_num)-1)
  ) ins
    on h.rut_asegurado = ins.rut_insured
left join (select * from cdp_dwh.dim_broker_t where src_sys_cd = 'axis') bro
on h.f_rut_corredor = bro.broker_id
left join (select * from cdp_dwh.dim_branch_office_t where src_sys_cd = 'axis') suc
on h.a_id_sucursal = suc.branch_office_id ) i
)
 
select * from (select s.*, row_number() over (partition by ssolicit 
order by b_max_sseguro desc nulls last, b_sseguro desc) as rnk from s) where rnk=1																			
)


/** added as part of DID_239 **/ 
select l.*,p.npoliza as policy_web from
 
(select k.*, case when (emission1=1 or emission_web=1) then 1 else 0 end as emission_or_web
from (
select j.*,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_SSEGURO end as B_SSEGURO_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_NPOLIZA end as B_NPOLIZA_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_NCERTIF end as B_NCERTIF_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_SPRODUC end as B_SPRODUC_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_IPIRIANUSEG end as B_IPIRIANUSEG_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_IPRITAR else B_IPRITAR end as B_IPRITAR_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_PDTOCOM else B_PDTOCOM end as B_PDTOCOM_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_IFRAQUSEG else B_IFRAQUSEG end as B_IFRAQUSEG_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_FEMISIO end as B_FEMISIO_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_FEFECTO end as B_FEFECTO_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_FIN_VIG end as B_FIN_VIG_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_FVENCIM else B_FVENCIM end as B_FVENCIM_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_CACTIVI end as B_CACTIVI_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_FANULAC end as B_FANULAC_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_TTITULO else B_TTITULO end as B_TTITULO_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_CAGENTE end as B_CAGENTE_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_ID_SUCURSAL else B_ID_SUCURSAL end as B_ID_SUCURSAL_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_NOMBRE_SUCURSAL else B_NOMBRE_SUCURSAL end as B_NOMBRE_SUCURSAL_1,
--case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_TBUSCAR else B_TBUSCAR end as B_TBUSCAR_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then translate(B_TBUSCAR,'#','') else translate(B_TBUSCAR,'#','') end as B_TBUSCAR_1, --modified as part of DID_238
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_NNUMNIF else B_NNUMNIF end as B_NNUMNIF_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_SPERSON else B_SPERSON end as B_SPERSON_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_CMARCA else B_CMARCA end as B_CMARCA_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_SMODELO else B_SMODELO end as B_SMODELO_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then B_NANOFAB else B_NANOFAB end as B_NANOFAB_1,
case when cusuari = 'FPIAXIS2' OR cusuari = 'ANIDA1' or (max_ssolicit is null and emission1 <> 1) then null else B_CSITUAC end as B_CSITUAC_1,
case when (sciclo_count>0)   then 1 else 0 end as emission_web
from (
select t1.*, t2.*,
case when (((max_ssolicit is not null and cnt_ssolicit>=1)) and cusuari <> 'FPIAXIS2' and cusuari <> 'ANIDA1')
then 1 else 0 end as emission1
from (
(select * from t) t1
left join (
select max(ssolicit) as max_ssolicit, count(ssolicit) as cnt_ssolicit, B_max_sseguro as B_max_sseguro_s3 from t
where B_max_sseguro is not null and cusuari <> 'FPIAXIS2' and cusuari <> 'ANIDA1' group by B_max_sseguro
) t2
on t1.ssolicit = t2.max_ssolicit)
) j
) k
)l /** added as part of DID_239 **/ left join cdp_ods.sisaxis_cmi_propuesta p 
   on cast(decode( l.CRFAAGE,'',null,l.CRFAAGE) as numeric)= p.sciclo  and
           p.csistema=1 and 
           p.ctipdoc=1  and 
           p.npoliza is not null

SELECT
STG.fact_quote_key,
STG.sol_id,

STG.src_sys_cd
FROM  cdp_dwh.fact_quotation_t_test STG
WHERE STG.src_sys_cd='axis'
